title: whcich Dao whould we have corporation first
body:
Bitcoin is the greatest reserve asset Olympus can use. Bitcoin has the clearest regulatory structure. Bitcoin is also still a nascent asset class that has a shot at absorbing over $100 trillion in value from other store-holds of wealth like stocks, bonds, collectibles, and real estate. For these reasons, Bitcoin has the highest expected value (risk-adjusted return). It should be a major part of the OlympusDAO treasury.

Proposal: Add as many ways as possible to let people bond bitcoin into the Olympus treasury. WBTC and renBTC are two examples of Ethereum-compatible forms of bitcoin.
